title: Nothing Extracted with Extract Outliers on GUI
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

### Operating System

Windows 11

### DeepLabCut version

dlc version 2.2.1.1

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

gpu NVIDA GeForce RTX3070

### Steps To Reproduce

I am attempting to extract outlier frames using the GUI. I do not understand what the error means.
